    "This BSC score is reflective of the posterior probability of that PAG.",
    "Finally, model averaging produces a single, non-deterministic, output PAG by considering the probability of each edge across all the PAGs.",
    "Jabbarri et al.",
    "(2017) found that the structural accuracy of RFCI-BSC was generally better than RFCI, with up to n = 70 variables and relatively small sample sizes of N = {200, 2000}, though it had worse adjacency accuracy with the largest number of variables.",
